{"tid":1680951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重點幫推, 從商必入, 食客都要入! ] 有關於黃/藍店分類","createTime":"2019-10-29T06:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T09:18:04.000Z","uid":216683,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"465cca40b936aaf42573166a02ad07b9c4064c61","tid":1680951,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:26:21.000Z","msg":"做到呢幾樣, 先叫係一間黃店<br />\n做唔到嘅, SORRY啦, 唔可以定義為黃店<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">食客</span>, 一定一定一定要跟據呢<span style=\"color: red;\">4大基本要求</span>, 去確定佢係咪一間黃店<br />\n無做好呢4點, 只能夠評估做藍店/淺藍店<br />\n點解無中立? 4個月, 你同我講中立? <br />\n<br />\n基本要求:<br />\n1. 有電視機嘅, 唔播TVB。唔撚洗講啦下話? 黃店播TVB? 唔好諗住關電視就算, 你有電視就一定要播港台, <span style=\"color: red;\">唔要再見到TVB係香港出現</span><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">要貼&quot;親黃&quot;嘅候選人單張</span>。 宜家去到11月尾都要貼住, 呢一樣野係基本, 你要話咩政見係自由, OK, 咁你就唔好做黃店, 宜家就係擺到明撐黃先支持架啦, 你唔撐, 點解我又要撐你先?<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">文宣最基本最基本, 都要有一句&quot;五大訴求, 缺一不可&quot;</span>, 你貼香港人加油, 藍絲都係香港人, 唔好同我係到玩走位<br />\n4. 遊行日你唔開鋪OK, 但開鋪最少都做下樣, 派下水, <span style=\"color: red;\">我要個IMAGE係間店係有支持過示威嘅</span>。你話唔洗成本呀D水? 哦, 咁你咪做返藍店, 呢幾箱水都攦唔到出黎? 少財唔出大財唔入呢一個唔洗教你啦下話, 生意人? 當日活動無去你個區嘅, 咪唔洗放出黎。講真, 放出黎都未必有人拎, 有可能仲會放低D錢係到, 呢樣野你唔做, 叫人點撐你間店?<br />\n<br />\n進階版本:<br />\n呢一樣, 你做咗就出名D, 多人食D, 但點都要基本要求有做好<br />\n1. 咩收益捐去612、星火個堆<br />\n2. 咩學生免費食<br />\n3. 罷工日齊罷工<br />\n4. 店鋪連儂牆<br />\n5. 人形畜牲不能內進<br />\n6. 大量新文宣, 會大大力宣傳黎緊嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係話你自己一句&quot;我係黃店&quot; 就係黃店</span><br />\n好多野都係要自己做出黎<br />\n同時間, 你要俾人知你係黃店, 你有做好4個基本要求<br />\n自然客似雲來, 唔好同我講你有隻米豬連貼紙就係黃店<br />\n自己PRINT出黎, 吉野家都係可以貼完話自己黃店<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好當人ON99, 無做好4大基本要求, 黃? 邊撚到黃呀?!</span><br />\n<br />\n大家記住, 只要間店有做好上面個四大基本要求<br />\n就可以認證做一間黃店<br />\n就算佢係扮黃, 佢都可以幫到個運動做宣傳<br />\n另一個角度睇, 都可以令到香港運動個IMAGE更大眾化<br />\n同時間, 有競爭才有進步, <span style=\"color: red;\">進階版本愈多人做間店就愈出名, 愈多人撐</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">愈早做足呢4大基本要求, 愈快多人知愈深入人心, 商機嘅野, 唔洗我教啦下話</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外真心多謝會肯支持嘅商鋪</span><br />\n講真, 香港真係要自救, 香港嘅食店好多都俾大集團食哂, 個個有利益關係想趕走小店<br />\n小店要走出一條路其實真係好難<br />\n但我地今次就係要自己人救自己人<br />\n我地食你間店, 同時間你都幫緊我地<br />\n互相幫助!!!"},{"pid":"92ca21c7d607b1d74eef65d4b1994a8b81832c3e","tid":1680951,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c49dac945bc7cd7039fcc0e7964d0e97642dd612","tid":1680951,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=29f4a9b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"6474f6cf135f61fe0d7553ce2261ec5b39d33504","tid":1680951,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"教大家一招KO林鄭成個取消區議會計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680857</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2932b7fa6eaf1d376d855f27ac18af221a79ab89","tid":1680951,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知米豬連個IDEA係好好<br />\n不過欠缺緊一個&quot;要求&quot; 同埋核實嘅過程<br />\n所以諗住呢一個無大台嘅認證要求出黎<br />\n基本要求洗唔洗再加落去, 提高個門檻, 真係睇大家點諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但上面嘅4個基本要求真係好重要, 亦都係最方便大家分出黃店嘅方式"},{"pid":"f00db9c0eb1babc84b3dc22333a61a3fd05e1126","tid":1680951,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以令到真真正正香港人嘅食店消失!!!<br />\n推呀!!!!"},{"pid":"1942c7d7c8bd0af50c6b3b0ed15cb91293d209fa","tid":1680951,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74447f7affba979e1b3da86517023369bb0c6a37","tid":1680951,"uid":189201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"呢個提議幾好<br />\n又易做, 支持"},{"pid":"f2ea3d9e73ca5603c37c5ddfd9d304ea50775d72","tid":1680951,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係奸商<br />\n搵香港人錢真係好易<br />\n只要做足呢四大基本要求, 基本上我零成本<br />\n但D客多到痴線, 做到手都軟<br />\n<br />\n相反藍絲D鋪? 講真, 靠班廢老做到幾多生意<br />\n低質素嘅人坐係間鋪到, 成間鋪都俾呢班人拉低哂個質素<br />\n變相無人想入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲想搵食?"},{"pid":"ffb93698dd786545435fabe2db207e35a7bda418","tid":1680951,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6c23daa08ada00dfa3182d28c1e641045c19f4","tid":1680951,"uid":254729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a7f04f966517d3996a2489d23fd2d635be4cb3","tid":1680951,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89d31482459aa29895ea2a58fbcb256fbb5412b1","tid":1680951,"uid":5672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但好似你話齋，張label阿豬阿狗都可以print出黎貼，你知喇，班狗閪藍店有咩做唔出為左錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我寧願攬炒，雖然黃店都跟住執，但都要班狗閪藍店陪葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe734d9944129aeea2a3a5a668b9697f2a9c7fe7","tid":1680951,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672823</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZDUJ9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZDUJ9a.jpg&h=394cb064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Whatsgap有貼紙認證啦 而家有各位貼紙師派緊同分工每個區 認住呢張poster 遲啲見到張貼紙就知道係黃店"}]}